---
layout: default.haml
title: Archive
description: The comprehensive list of every blog post I've written.
---

.archive.text-content
  %h2 Archive
  - each year in archive
    %table
      %thead
        %th{ colspan: "2", align: "left" }= year.year
      %tbody
        - each post in year.data
          %tr
            %td{ align: "left", width: "64", valign: "top" }= printDate(post.date, "MMM D")
            %td{ align: "left", valign: "top" }
              %a{ href: urlTo(post) }= post.title
